{"tid":162352,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"癲狗系列 - 肉絲炒麵","createTime":"2017-03-19T08:21:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-22T00:02:05.000Z","uid":74981,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"33699331c9001647edf42d3a74954426e90e8fd3","tid":162352,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T08:21:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/524f769319617d61f5ffe54de7e793cf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2F524f769319617d61f5ffe54de7e793cf.jpg&h=3541c91a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網址如下:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NJNoE6zo6JQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNJNoE6zo6JQ&d=Bs0XXOgOekCAei%2FiISrrFjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=b90f81ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NJNoE6zo6JQ</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n做法概述:<br />\n1. 炒麵一個滾水煮幾分鐘, 過冷河, king乾水備用<br />\n2. 梅頭瘦肉洗淨切絲, 用1茶匙米酒同1茶匙生抽加少少豆粉同水醃15分鐘<br />\n3.開油鍋, 油溫5-6成, 落麵炸, 用中小火, 開始脆身, 轉d大個火炸脆, 然後反一反再炸脆<br />\n4. 上碟<br />\n5.倒淨少少油, 落幾粒蒜頭爆香, 落瘦肉炒, 再落銀芽九王炒, 落大半碗水大火煮滾<br />\n6. 收細火, 落4份1茶匙鹽, 4份1茶匙糖, 少少胡椒粉, 攪勻, 再落豆粉水埋芡<br />\n7. 將所有汁連材料鋪係炒面上, 完成"},{"pid":"67e9eb5928c91c5dc9c84bc605c4a49e93a2fd99","tid":162352,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T08:22:37.000Z","msg":"狗又炒野喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b2191ff304f76ac133f0aa84eaae12193dfae7a","tid":162352,"uid":1436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T08:22:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80c7cedd7a50a71c48d074ab9e5ea1bb2e037c71","tid":162352,"uid":1436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T08:22:58.000Z","msg"